<!-- Our Story Section -->
<div class="row mb-5">
    <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4">
        <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-body p-4">
                <h2 class="card-title text-primary mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-heart me-2"></i>
                    Our Story
                </h2>
                <p class="card-text text-justify">
                    Founded with a passion for literature and learning, BookStore began as a small local bookshop with a simple mission: 
                    to connect readers with the books that would inspire, educate, and entertain them. What started as a humble collection 
                    of carefully curated titles has grown into a comprehensive online destination for book lovers worldwide.
                </p>
                <p class="card-text text-justify">
                    Our journey has been driven by the belief that books have the power to transform lives, broaden perspectives, 
                    and bring people together. Every book in our collection is selected with care, ensuring that we offer only 
                    the finest literature, educational materials, and entertainment for our valued customers.
                </p>
                <p class="card-text text-justify">
                    Today, we're proud to serve thousands of customers globally, maintaining the same personal touch and attention 
                    to quality that has defined us from the beginning.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4">
        <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-body p-4 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center text-center">
                <div class="mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-quote-left fa-3x text-primary opacity-50 mb-3"></i>
                    <blockquote class="blockquote">
                        <p class="mb-3 fs-5 fst-italic">
                            "A room without books is like a body without a soul."
                        </p>
                        <footer class="blockquote-footer">
                            <cite title="Source Title">Marcus Tullius Cicero</cite>
                        </footer>
                    </blockquote>
                </div>
                <div class="reading-illustration">
                    <i class="fas fa-book-reader fa-5x text-primary opacity-75"></i>
                    <p class="mt-3 text-muted">Fostering a love for reading in every customer</p>
                </div>
            </div>
